.cs 7 on
.item 'SET SUGNO Command' 'Added on 07/08/82 by LSO'
.boxon
SET SUGNO [nnnn]
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
Required Privileges:  without suggestion number -- NONE
                      with suggestion number    -- SYSTEMS

The SET SUGNO command is used to set the last suggestion number.

.* SELECT 'SET SUGNO Command Options'
.us Option Description

.* OPTION nnnn
.ix nnnn 'on SET SUGNO Command'
nnnn\\\\\\\\\\\specifies the suggestion number that the last suggestion number
                should be set to.  If ommited (which is the unprivileged
                mode), the last suggestion number will be incremented.
.cs 7 off
